channel.title: What to write
channel.description: Ok, theirs a lot of you with good servers that you made mostly yourself, but what I'm asking is what's something good to code for practice or beginners, I've read tutorials and books on Java and all that good stuff, and edited my server a bunch, but I want something to call my own, like whats a good skill or mini game or something to code to start? You get what I'm saying?
